        "action": "Ban dogs from cemeteries (excluding guide dogs)",
        "additional_details": "Ban dogs from walking through cemetery's either with or without leash it's totally unnecessary for people to walk their dogs through a place where people are laid to rest.\r\n\r\nMany of times I have been in cemeteries and noticed people letting their dogs run over the graves of service men & women, adults, babies & recently buried graves.\r\n\r\nNot only this some owners let the dogs urinate on headstones & litter their business on grave sides without picking it up after.",
        "background": "Place a ban on dogs being walked through cemeteries, excluding guide dogs.",
